            <title>[CASSANDRA-19115] Avoid bad serializedSize when sending GOSSIP_SHUTDOWN message</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-19115</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
